item.title: CVE-2021-24268|2024-08-03T19:28:22.758Z -- unknown -- jetwidgets%20for%20elementor
item.description: The “JetWidgets For Elementor” WordPress Plugin before 1.0.9 has several widgets that are vulnerable to stored Cross-Site Scripting (XSS) by lower-privileged users such as contributors, all via a similar method.
